<% layout('/layouts/boilerplate') -%>
<div class="container py-5">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="text-center mb-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-4">About Wanderlust</h1>
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead text-muted">Wanderlust connects travelers with unique accommodations and authentic experiences around the world. We're on a mission to help people discover the joy of travel while empowering local hosts to share their spaces and cultures.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <div class="row align-items-center mb-5 py-4">
    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
      <div class="position-relative">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073771259-6a8506099945" alt="Scenic Mountain View" class="img-fluid rounded-4 shadow-lg" style="object-fit: cover;">
        <div class="position-absolute" style="bottom: -20px; right: -20px; z-index: -1; width: 100%; height: 100%; background-color: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.1; border-radius: 1rem;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6 ps-lg-5">
      <h2 class="mb-4" style="color: var(--primary-color);">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Wanderlust was founded in 2020 by a group of passionate travelers who believed that the best way to experience a new place is by living like a local. What started as a small community of homeStays in India has grown into a global platform connecting travelers with unique accommodations worldwide.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Our journey began when we noticed that many travelers were seeking more authentic and immersive experiences than traditional hotels could offer. We set out to create a platform where hosts could share their unique spaces and local knowledge, while travelers could discover destinations through the eyes of those who call it home.</p>
      <p>Today, Wanderlust hosts thousands of listings across India and beyond, from urban apartments to countryside retreats, each offering a distinctive glimpse into local life and culture.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Our Values Section -->
  <div class="row py-4 mb-5">
    <div class="col-12 text-center mb-5">
      <h2 style="color: var(--primary-color);">Our Values</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm hover-card">
        <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
          <div class="icon-circle mb-4 mx-auto">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-hands-holding-circle fs-3" style="color: var(--secondary-color);"></i>
          </div>
          <h4 class="card-title mb-3">Community</h4>
          <p class="card-text text-muted">We believe in the power of human connection. Our platform brings together people from diverse backgrounds, creating a global community of hosts and travelers who share experiences, stories, and cultures. We prioritize building relationships that extend beyond transactions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm hover-card">
        <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
          <div class="icon-circle mb-4 mx-auto">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-leaf fs-3" style="color: var(--secondary-color);"></i>
          </div>
          <h4 class="card-title mb-3">Sustainability</h4>
          <p class="card-text text-muted">We're committed to promoting responsible travel that respects both local communities and the environment. By encouraging travelers to engage with local economies and cultural practices, we aim to support sustainable tourism that benefits everyone involved while minimizing ecological impact.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm hover-card">
        <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
          <div class="icon-circle mb-4 mx-auto">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles fs-3" style="color: var(--secondary-color);"></i>
          </div>
          <h4 class="card-title mb-3">Authenticity</h4>
          <p class="card-text text-muted">We celebrate the unique character of every place and person. Our platform showcases genuine experiences that reflect local cultures and traditions. We encourage hosts to share what makes their homes and neighborhoods special, and we help travelers discover the authentic heart of each destination.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
